        "title": "Setouchi inter-island cargo network reaches 4,200 sorties",
        "excerpt": "The network now spans 28 automated stations across the Hiroshima–Ehime corridor, achieving a 99.4% on-time delivery rate. Cargo volumes have grown 340% year-on-year, validating the viability of persistent autonomous logistics in maritime archipelagos.",
